You are given an array arr[] of N integers including 0. The task is to find the smallest positive number missing from the array.


=====================================================================================================================
 static int missingNumber(int arr[], int size)
    {
        // Your code here
        Arrays.sort(arr);
         int ans=1;
        for(int i=0;i<size;i++){
            if(arr[i]==ans){
                ans++;
            }
        }
        return ans;
    }
